{"tid":569286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[非毒撚專利！]一代亞洲影后李菁 家中暴斃數天無人知","createTime":"2018-02-22T14:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T05:28:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da65ebee59e74982719b90fb4de629898b7f6b1e","tid":569286,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"今日下午4時，鰂魚涌海光街海光苑一個單位，傳出嚴重惡臭，保安見狀報警。消防員到場破門入屋，發現一名69歲女子暴斃，屍身亦嚴重腐爛。警方在單位內撿獲身份證明文件，發現死者名為李國瑛（即李菁的真名）。經初步調查後，警方認為案件無可疑，列作屍體發現案處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>17歲憑《魚美人》揚威亞洲影展<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n一代亞洲影后李菁，自幼對電影有興趣，讀中學時聽聞邵氏所屬的「南國實驗劇團」招收學員，於是報考，更成功獲取錄。1965年，年僅17歲的李菁憑電影《魚美人》獲第12屆亞洲影展「最佳女主角金禾獎」，而於1972年電影《娃娃夫人》她亦擔任女主角，並憑此片榮獲第18屆亞洲影展「最受歡迎女星金藝像獎」，因此亦被稱為「娃娃影后」及「亞洲影后」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1227566/xlarge/8932a5fd48878bf3222d59183b9f04de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1227566%2Fxlarge%2F8932a5fd48878bf3222d59183b9f04de.jpg&h=e8f54c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/162202/-%E5%86%8D%E8%A6%8B%E6%9D%8E%E8%8F%81-%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%BD%B1%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%8E%E8%8F%81-%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9A%B4%E6%96%83%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E7%9F%A5-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B469%E6%AD%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F162202%2F-%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%258F%2581-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%2590%258E%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%258F%2581-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%2596%2583%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259F%25A5-%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B9%25B469%25E6%25AD%25B2&d=6Ibac1x%2BSHndQM8TaMg4W5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=ed70b3d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/162202/-%E5%86%8D%E8%A6%8B%E6%9D%8E%E8%8F%81-%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A